Class LinkedQueue<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • binaryTree.LinkedQueue<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Queue<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>

    public class LinkedQueue<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Queue<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>
    Realization of a FIFO queue as an adaptation of a SinglyLinkedList. All operations are performed in constant time.
    See Also:
    SinglyLinkedList
